dataObject.content: Facebook Chief Operating Officer Sheryl Sandberg has recently donated $1 million to Planned Parenthood Action Fund. In an interview with HuffPost, Sandberg said she was motivated by the "draconian laws" protecting unborn children recently passed in red states like Alabama, Missouri, and Georgia.
